attributes.review: So I opened this app only to see that it was automatically glitching. I then had to wait 30 minutes before finally giving up and closing it. As soon as I exited it(mind you I was outside) all of the trees started to get ripped out of the ground, start levitating in mid air, and began chanting Cheetos. By this point I am pissing myself because how freaked out I am when suddenly the most terrifying thing appeared. Down the street I see the Cheeto man (aka Donald trump) holding a bag of Cheetos who are his distant relatives, sprinting towards me, laughing like a complete and utter psychopath. Scared as I am, I jump into one of the levitating trees and to hide. Then, my phone reopened this app without me doing anything and once it opened it made Donald trump even more of a mad man as he looked right to where I was in the tree when finally I come to my senses and exited this app once more and deleted it and everything when back to normal. So overall, I would highly suggest not downloading this app for your own good.
